<title>USA: Invacare raises Healthdyne bid.</title>
<headline>Invacare raises Healthdyne bid.</headline>
<dateline>ELYRIA, Ohio 1997-03-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Invacare Corp said on Monday it has increased its tender offer for Healthdyne Technologies Inc's common stock to $13.50 a share from $13.</p>
<p>Invacare has extended the tender offer to April 28, 1997, it said.  </p>
<p>Officials of Healthdyne, which makes medical devices, were not immediately available for comment. On March 25, the company said it considered Invacare's $13-a-share offer &quot;inadequate.&quot;</p>
